--- !u!114 &1511107868
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1511107867}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fc9aac3b0b6524b40997582034e275a6, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  IntroDi: 1
  dialogueText: {fileID: 779891243}
  dialogueSets:
  - lines:
    - name: 3
      text: Hey! Welcome to {w}heck{ }! my name's Ivanna, I'm the {s}Devil{ }.
    - name: 3
      text: And {w}youuuuu{ } borrowed 20 bucks from me for your gun. I want my money
        back, with interest.
    - name: 3
      text: let me run some numbers really quick...
    - name: 3
      text: ...
    - name: 3
      text: ...
    - name: 3
      text: and after all the interest... it's about... $10,000.99!
    - name: 0
      text: ...{s}what????{ }
    - name: 0
      text: What kind of interest rate does it have for $20 to turn into {s}$10,000?!?!{
        }
    - name: 3
      text: Aboooout... 372.9%.
    - name: 3
      text: but since I'm {w}soooo{ } nice, i'll drop the 99 cents.
    - name: 3
      text: if you ever need any help, come talk to me.
  - lines:
    - name: 3
      text: ...need help already?
    - name: 3
      text: geez...
    - name: 0
      text: sorry?
    - name: 3
      text: just head to the store to the right and buy something from there.
    - name: 3
      text: your health and money are linked, so the fact that you're even alive
        means you have some money.
  - lines:
    - name: 3
      text: you should also learn how to use the bank.
    - name: 0
      text: the building on the left, right?
    - name: 3
      text: sorry?
    - name: 3
      text: just head to the store and buy something from there.
    - name: 3
      text: your health and money are linked, so the fact that you're even alive
        means you have some money.
  - lines:
    - name: 3
      text: ...need help already?
    - name: 3
      text: geez...
    - name: 0
      text: sorry?
    - name: 3
      text: just head to the store and buy something from there.
    - name: 3
      text: your health and money are linked, so the fact that you're even alive
        means you have some money.
  speed: 0.04
  dialogueActive: 0
